Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大男生合伙来欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙真是差劲  差劲透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊  远坂  这跟你又没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们也来对我做同样的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不就和我有关系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须保持平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想操控魔力必须要时刻控制好自己的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果操控有误  魔力会反噬自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过度的力量与错误的方法不仅对自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会给身边的人带来危害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻牢记正确的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是远坂家的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「时刻保持从容  优雅处事」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到这种事琴音可不能忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果错在他们的话  你可得发发脾气才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛真是厉害  敢那么直接地说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢  这是很普通的事情吧  或者说理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  这都是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲  再多教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要怎么才能做出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  对于现在的凛来说或许有些难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  只要凛你每天努力  总有一天能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  你可是远坂家的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  小凛  这个地方可不可以教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个在教科书的23页有写
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边只是在这里计算错误了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问题嘛…你看  和这个例题是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  凛好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来坐下  我按顺序教你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要去禅城那边住才行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦圣杯战争开始  冬木市就已不算安全之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帮父亲赢得圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛  不能给爸爸添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是累赘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非如此  这次要以比过去更齐全的准备来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中也包含了确保你们的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此凛和妈妈最好还是离开冬木市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  只是父亲还没有教给我足够的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我自己学就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完…完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.15,up,NTP,0,0,0,,启此门者为何许人也？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.97,up,NTP,0,0,0,,或可为吾友朋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.85,up,NTP,0,0,0,,执吾之手  以此为誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.48,up,NTP,0,0,0,,相会于吾陋室之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:38.80,up,NTP,0,0,0,,汝之手   是小？是大？是瘦？是硬？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.15,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,Du,  wer die Tür geöffnet hat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.97,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,wird  freunde  sein
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.85,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,Für die Aussage nimm meine Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.48,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,wir  werden  in  meinem  Zimmer  treffen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:38.80,bird,NTP,0,0,0,,Sind deine Hände, Klein? Gross? Schlank? Steif?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得把书合上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对凛来说  要看这本书还为时过早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上有些东西自身就带有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫魔力针
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然平时不会有任何反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果附近有魔术的痕迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛  你用魔力发动它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后对于刚才那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有这种反应的东西是凛还无法应付的  必须小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这个送给凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算提前送你的生日礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等圣杯战争结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让你尝试一下更为正式的宝石魔术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于  异变开始产生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是自习哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上的新闻也是绑架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}最近冬木市经常发生儿童突然失踪的案件…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师他们一直在开会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天第五节课不上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但老师说得呆在家里不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是绑架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被绑架的都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗体好像没有放进棺材里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟样子很凄惨啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案件的确是在冬木市发生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是和琴音同班的远坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在电话无人接听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在听到「嘀」的一声后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…夜晚的冬木市？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和白天完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人感觉好不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没见过这样的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是说到处都有魔力的痕迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得找到琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这么晚了还带着孩子外出？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险  要是被发现了肯定会被送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  小心点走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩的数量变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要躲起来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去  什么也做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被下了什么魔术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？怎么  迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们正准备开派对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人数还有点不够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要也来帮帮忙呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  这种事就得人多才热闹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑什么跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是用那手镯  把大家给…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:15:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要破坏掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  你还是愿意帮忙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可没时间哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下估计要挨老爷骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  小凛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了啊  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有这种反应的东西是凛还无法应付的  必须小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛…没想到竟然会去了冬木市…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛她没事  只是睡过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雁夜君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是间桐家的魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以肉体为巢穴  以灵魂为食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这些代价才能换来如此的魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小樱会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她变成这样之前  我一定会将她救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脏砚想要的只有圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他答应我只要能得到那东西  他便会放了小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说…圣杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Servant是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于现在的小樱来说  就连抱有希望也是一种折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  请你代替那孩子祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也为了小樱的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雁夜君  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:20:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天  我们能回到当初一起在这个公园嬉戏的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候  小凛和小樱也会重新成为姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  葵  你也不必再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雁夜君  你是想死吗？要和时臣同归于尽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮礼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着远坂时臣的夫人和千金不管  真的妥当么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续监视Berserker的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是小事  但我也确实能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要说这样就能独当一面吧  我却又半途就晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我还不够成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这也只是现在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有足够的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天  我会以远坂的魔术师这个身份开始战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这随时可能到来的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要勤学苦练  谨记父亲的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时只需要将自己所能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力又优雅地完成就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有欲望的王者连装饰品都不如！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能保护弱者的话  又有什么意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有任何损失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是固有结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本王要亲手杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是想要征服世…哇！
